 Z‚ÜêFPS ANIMATEDSVG ARGS;START;END;T;LA;LO;JD1;JD2;NDAYS;I;S;FJ;FJS;CX;CY;R;PAD;FMT;NSTARS;NBRIGHT;BRIGHTIDX;NPI;ALLPC;PLAN_PX;PLAN_PY;PLAN_VIS;PLAN_RAH;PLAN_RAM;PLAN_DEC;PLAN_ALT;PLAN_AZ;PLAN_MX;PLAN_MY;PHASES;PCHARS;NAMES;NM;BN;TY;VHEIGHT;SR;COL;LATD;LATM;NS;LONGD;LONGM;EW;H;AP;MN2;PLANJSON
‚çù Generate animated SVG with JavaScript-driven animation
‚çù FPS: playback frames per second
‚çù ARGS: (M D Y)(M D Y) TIME LAT LONG
‚çù Returns character vector containing complete animated SVG
‚çù
‚çù Stars are computed in JavaScript (ported sky math).
‚çù Planet positions are pre-computed in APL and embedded as JSON.

‚çù === PARSE ARGS ===
 START END T LA LO‚ÜêARGS
 JD1‚ÜêJNU START
 JD2‚ÜêJNU END
 NDAYS‚Üê1+JD2-JD1

‚çù Map constants (same as PLOTSVG)
 PAD‚Üê80
 CX‚ÜêPAD+1080 ‚ãÑ CY‚ÜêPAD+1080 ‚ãÑ R‚Üê1080
 FMT‚Üê{‚çï‚åä0.5+‚çµ}
 FJS‚Üê{'¬Ø'‚éïR'-'‚ä¢‚çï‚çµ}
 FJ‚Üê{1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®FJS¬®‚çµ}

‚çù Star info
 NSTARS‚Üê‚äÉ‚ç¥STARS
 BRIGHTIDX‚Üê‚ç∏BRIGHT
 NBRIGHT‚Üê‚â¢BRIGHTIDX

‚çù === COLLECT PLANET DATA ===
 PLAN_PX‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_PY‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_VIS‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_RAH‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_RAM‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_DEC‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_ALT‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_AZ‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_MX‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PLAN_MY‚ÜêNDAYS 11‚ç¥0
 PHASES‚ÜêNDAYS‚ç¥0

 ‚éï‚Üê'Computing ',(‚çïNDAYS),' frames...'
 :For I :In ‚ç≥NDAYS
   STATEDDAYNO‚ÜêJD1+I-1
   STATEDTIME‚ÜêT
   LAT‚ÜêLA ‚ãÑ LONG‚ÜêLO
   TIME‚ÜêLO TIMEADJUST T
   DATE‚ÜêSTATEDDAYNO+(TIME√∑24)-LO√∑360

   CALCULATEPLANETS
   NPI‚Üê‚äÉ‚ç¥PLANETS

‚çù Expand visible-only planet coords to full matrix
   ALLPC‚ÜêNPI 2‚ç¥0
   :If ‚à®/VP
     ALLPC[‚ç∏VP;]‚ÜêPLANETCOORD
   :EndIf

‚çù Pad to 11 rows if no comet
   :If NPI<11
     PLANETS‚ÜêPLANETS,[1](11-NPI) 3‚ç¥0
     PLANETAA‚ÜêPLANETAA,[1](11-NPI) 2‚ç¥¬Ø90 0
     VP‚ÜêVP,(11-NPI)‚ç¥0
     ALLPC‚ÜêALLPC,[1](11-NPI) 2‚ç¥0
   :EndIf

   PLAN_PX[I;]‚Üê‚åä0.5+CX+R√óALLPC[;1]
   PLAN_PY[I;]‚Üê‚åä0.5+CY-R√óALLPC[;2]
   PLAN_VIS[I;]‚ÜêVP
   PLAN_RAH[I;]‚Üê‚åäPLANETS[;1]
   PLAN_RAM[I;]‚Üê‚åä0.5+60√óPLANETS[;1]-PLAN_RAH[I;]
   PLAN_DEC[I;]‚Üê‚åä0.5+PLANETS[;2]
   PLAN_ALT[I;]‚Üê‚åä0.5+PLANETAA[;1]
   PLAN_AZ[I;]‚Üê‚åä0.5+PLANETAA[;2]
   PLAN_MX[I;]‚Üê0.01√ó‚åä0.5+100√óALLPC[;1]
   PLAN_MY[I;]‚Üê0.01√ó‚åä0.5+100√óALLPC[;2]
   PHASES[I]‚ÜêPHASE
 :EndFor
 ‚éï‚Üê'Building SVG...'

‚çù === TITLE BASE ===
 LATD‚Üê‚åä|LA ‚ãÑ LATM‚Üê‚åä0.5+60√ó(|LA)-LATD
 NS‚Üê(1+LA<0)‚äÉ'NORTH' 'SOUTH'
 LONGD‚Üê‚åä|LO ‚ãÑ LONGM‚Üê‚åä0.5+60√ó(|LO)-LONGD
 EW‚Üê(1+LO>0)‚äÉ'WEST' 'EAST'
 H‚Üê12|T
 :If H=0 ‚ãÑ H‚Üê12 ‚ãÑ :EndIf
 AP‚Üê(1+T<12)‚äÉ'PM' 'AM'
 MN2‚Üê‚çï‚åä0.5+60√óH-‚åäH
 :If 1=‚â¢MN2 ‚ãÑ MN2‚Üê'0',MN2 ‚ãÑ :EndIf

‚çù === FORMAT PLANET DATA AS JSON ===
 PLANJSON‚Üê''
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"px":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_PX),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"py":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_PY),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"vis":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_VIS),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"rah":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_RAH),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"ram":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_RAM),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"dec":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_DEC),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"alt":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_ALT),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"az":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_AZ),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"mx":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_MX),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"my":[',(1‚Üì‚àä',',¬®{'[',(FJ ‚çµ),']'}¬®‚Üì‚çâPLAN_MY),'],'
 PLANJSON,‚Üê'"phase":[',(FJ PHASES),']'

‚çù === BUILD SVG ===
‚çù Compute total height: planet table + 22 bright star rows
 TY‚ÜêPAD+2160+120
 TY‚ÜêTY+50+8+32+(11√ó34)+10+60
 TY‚ÜêTY+50+8+32+(NBRIGHT√ó34)
 VHEIGHT‚ÜêTY+PAD

‚çù SVG header
 Z‚Üê'<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 ',(‚çï2160+2√óPAD),' ',(‚çïVHEIGHT),'"'
 Z,‚Üê' width="',(‚çï2160+2√óPAD),'" height="',(‚çïVHEIGHT),'">'
 Z,‚Üê'<defs><style>'
 Z,‚Üê'text{font-family:monospace;fill:#ccc}'
 Z,‚Üê'.bright{fill:#ffd700}'
 Z,‚Üê'.faint{fill:#aaa}'
 Z,‚Üê'.star-label{font-size:28px;fill:#ffd700}'
 Z,‚Üê'.planet{fill:#4fc3f7;font-size:36px}'
 Z,‚Üê'.planet-label{font-size:24px;fill:#4fc3f7}'
 Z,‚Üê'.cardinal{font-size:40px;fill:#888;text-anchor:middle;dominant-baseline:central}'
 Z,‚Üê'.legend{font-size:22px;fill:#999}'
 Z,‚Üê'.title{font-size:26px;fill:#999;text-anchor:middle}'
 Z,‚Üê'.table-header{font-size:28px;fill:#bbb;text-anchor:middle}'
 Z,‚Üê'.table-text{font-size:26px;fill:#999}'
 Z,‚Üê'.table-hdr-r{font-size:26px;fill:#bbb;text-anchor:end}'
 Z,‚Üê'.table-r{font-size:26px;fill:#999;text-anchor:end}'
 Z,‚Üê'</style></defs>'

‚çù Background
 Z,‚Üê'<rect width="',(‚çï2160+2√óPAD),'" height="',(‚çïVHEIGHT),'" fill="#0a0a1a"/>'

‚çù Title (JS updates content)
 Z,‚Üê'<text class="title" id="title" x="',(‚çïPAD+1080),'" y="',(‚çïPAD-20),'"> </text>'

‚çù Crosshairs
 Z,‚Üê'<g stroke="#333" stroke-width="1">'
 Z,‚Üê'<line x1="',(‚çïPAD),'" y1="',(‚çïCY),'" x2="',(‚çïPAD+2160),'" y2="',(‚çïCY),'"/>'
 Z,‚Üê'<line x1="',(‚çïCX),'" y1="',(‚çïPAD),'" x2="',(‚çïCX),'" y2="',(‚çïPAD+2160),'"/>'
 Z,‚Üê'</g>'

‚çù Horizon circle
 Z,‚Üê'<circle cx="',(‚çïCX),'" cy="',(‚çïCY),'" r="',(‚çïR),'" fill="none" stroke="#555" stroke-width="2"/>'

‚çù Cardinals
 Z,‚Üê'<text class="cardinal" x="',(‚çïCX),'" y="',(FMT CY-R-20),'">N</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'<text class="cardinal" x="',(‚çïCX),'" y="',(FMT CY+R+35),'">S</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'<text class="cardinal" x="',(FMT CX-R-25),'" y="',(‚çïCY),'">E</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'<text class="cardinal" x="',(FMT CX+R+25),'" y="',(‚çïCY),'">W</text>'

‚çù Zenith marker
 Z,‚Üê'<circle cx="',(‚çïCX),'" cy="',(‚çïCY),'" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.5"/>'

‚çù Legend
 Z,‚Üê'<g class="legend" transform="translate(',(‚çïPAD+40),',',(‚çïPAD+2160+10),')">'
 Z,‚Üê'<circle class="bright" cx="0" cy="0" r="8"/><text x="16" y="6">bright</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'<circle class="faint" cx="120" cy="0" r="3"/><text x="130" y="6">faint</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'<circle cx="230" cy="0" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="242" y="6">zenith</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'<text x="350" y="6" fill="#555">‚Äî horizon</text>'
 Z,‚Üê'</g>'

‚çù === STAR ELEMENTS (JS updates cx, cy, visibility) ===
 :For I :In ‚ç≥NSTARS
   :If BRIGHT[I]
     SR‚Üê8 ‚ãÑ COL‚Üê'bright'
   :Else
     SR‚Üê3 ‚ãÑ COL‚Üê'faint'
   :EndIf
   Z,‚Üê'<circle class="',COL,'" id="s',(‚çïI-1),'" cx="0" cy="0" r="',(‚çïSR),'" visibility="hidden"/>'
 :EndFor

